rr.error

Class ErrorMessages

  • java.lang.Object
    • rr.error.ErrorMessages

  • public class ErrorMessages
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper routines for managing error messages on the most common syntactic categories. The categories are all the same -- see methods for a description.
